<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>跑跑卡丁车 on Orztu The Way | Orz途</title><link>https://www.orztu.com/tags/%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%81%E8%BD%A6/</link><description>Recent content in 跑跑卡丁车 on Orztu The Way | Orz途</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>Orztu The Way</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2019 17:52:17 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.orztu.com/tags/%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%81%E8%BD%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>跑跑卡丁车手游 L1 驾照“下坡漂移”教程</title><link>https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2019 17:52:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;a class="link" href="popkart-l1-4-cut.mp4" >&amp;raquo;&amp;gt;视频地址&amp;laquo;&amp;lt;&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>首先我们要在前两个门集满第一管氮气。&lt;br>
1号门前向右轻打方向调整车头，然后向左拖漂。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01_hu_c4b4207654cd8bb9.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01_hu_8532f219721d9cbc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>右漂经过2号门然后向左拉正车头后使用第一个氮气。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02_hu_92a3a7883545580.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02_hu_b4e01eda283fe370.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>立即向右拖漂经过3号门。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03_hu_241914462688a894.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03_hu_2ae28575d6723d27.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>氮气满之后马上拉正车头。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04_hu_7b25b729268816c8.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04_hu_655376fe84d7a1bd.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>继续使用氮气，然后拖漂经过4号门，同样气满之后回正。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05_hu_aeb417a6b74e6e35.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05_hu_bb53bcd89dabd2ff.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>趁氮气未结束，再次拖漂经过5号门，然后马上使用氮气。&lt;br>
5号门相对前面两个门不用漂那么大。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06_hu_48ff3597bc41ae9d.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06_hu_d1c550b2e7087ac9.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>过了5号门氮气满了断位拉头，然后接左漂继续集气并过6号门。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07_hu_2c3094bbd88c4567.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07_hu_675aaa728a9642f6.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08_hu_a1c4231125b7039.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08_hu_bc70ef1a9c799deb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>7号门前这个小坎需要小漂一下，不然落地容易弹起。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09_hu_797daa4a140e1b4c.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09_hu_d3d42ae47a41722c.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>落地走一点点之后，向左轻漂，不要太大。&lt;br>
因为已经有两个氮气了，漂满了这一管就浪费了。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10_hu_a055789a6c521eeb.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10_hu_f24fd5ebd193f6f3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>过这个坎向右轻漂，然后落地马上使用氮气。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11_hu_9adb4d9697eaeca8.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11_hu_e9caf831296f333d.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12_hu_230a0268949fb7f0.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12_hu_4e1aeaf5696fe60f.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>然后把刚才没满的氮气漂满，这样又有两个氮气了。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13_hu_b6d49122a1c94bcc.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13_hu_3b58bbc46435a5fb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>紧接着再次把氮气漂到快满，以便下坡起跳之后集气。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14_hu_66cf09c6aed57f24.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14_hu_85dd118bc821b5da.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>使用氮气加速下坡，起跳前向左轻漂，不要用力。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15_hu_e57b8240f7c8c5d4.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15_hu_bf6ade6f930dad22.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>落地之后氮气满了马上使用氮气纠正车头，避免撞墙；&lt;br>
如果前面失误，这个时候没有氮气，可以再次向左漂避免撞墙。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16_hu_205ed218fcf0d567.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16_hu_fa10b64333379593.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>这个坎前向右漂移过弯，同样满了就用氮气回正；&lt;br>
如果没有氮气可用，就向左拉车头集气，然后使用氮气。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17_hu_34c101a9689ad241.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17_hu_a2ec7e5ee8a64b5e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>下一个弯车速起来就向左拖漂过弯，并集满一管气。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18_hu_7598551585699c7e.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18_hu_96d1680260067f49.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>出弯后使用氮气，调整位置，准备从外道插入下一个弯。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19_hu_25c7f96e48eecd11.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19_hu_469e272a6be7d97e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>这个弯向右打死，出弯使用氮气或者断位拉头。-&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20_hu_10d5dfd590bf0228.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20_hu_7c79de6eaf359216.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>出弯之后等速度起来拖漂过最后一个弯。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21_hu_8f50ff00b0249430.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21_hu_75a8d866ec49d926.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>最后一下起跳前向左轻漂。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22_hu_6c799cf29374d85f.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22_hu_d501a92b4437b2ab.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>剩余的直线就交给氮气了。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23_hu_efa62a5c0cde9a4e.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23_hu_9eb41b6ba0d9933a.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>&lt;a class="link" href="popkart-l1-4-cut.mp4" >&amp;raquo;&amp;gt;视频地址&amp;laquo;&amp;lt;&lt;/a>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>$ N_{2}O $ 本是笑气，但在跑跑里面被大家称为“氮气”&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote></description></item></channel></rss>